export const LANG_FRAMEWORK={nl:"CEFR",de:"CEFR",fr:"CEFR",es:"CEFR",zh:"HSK",ja:"JLPT",ko:"TOPIK"};
export const getUnitStandard=(unit,lang)=>{
  const fw=LANG_FRAMEWORK[lang]||"CEFR";
  const std=STANDARDS[fw];
  if(!std||!unit.objectives||!unit.objectives.length)return{framework:fw,level:unit.level||null,derived:false};
  const levels=std.levels;
  let maxIdx=-1;
  for(const ok of unit.objectives){
    const lv=std.objectives[ok];
    if(lv){const idx=levels.indexOf(lv);if(idx>maxIdx)maxIdx=idx;}
  }
  return{framework:fw,level:maxIdx>=0?levels[maxIdx]:unit.level||null,derived:maxIdx>=0};
};
export const getObjectiveStandard=(okId,framework)=>{
  const obj=OBJECTIVES[okId];
  if(!obj||!obj.standards)return null;
  return obj.standards[framework]||null;
};
export const deriveUnitStandard=(unit,framework)=>{
  if(!unit.objectives||!unit.objectives.length)return null;
  const std=STANDARDS[framework];
  if(!std)return null;
  const levels=std.levels;
  let maxIdx=-1;
  for(const ok of unit.objectives){
    const obj=OBJECTIVES[ok];
    if(obj&&obj.standards&&obj.standards[framework]){
      const idx=levels.indexOf(obj.standards[framework]);
      if(idx>maxIdx)maxIdx=idx;
    }
  }
  return maxIdx>=0?levels[maxIdx]:null;
};
export const explainUnitLevel=(unit,framework)=>{
  if(!unit.objectives||!unit.objectives.length)return{level:unit.level,derived:false,objectives:[]};
  const std=STANDARDS[framework];
  if(!std)return{level:unit.level,derived:false,objectives:[]};
  const levels=std.levels;
  const items=[];
  let maxIdx=-1;
  for(const ok of unit.objectives){
    const obj=OBJECTIVES[ok];
    if(!obj)continue;
    const lv=obj.standards?obj.standards[framework]:std.objectives[ok];
    if(!lv)continue;
    const idx=levels.indexOf(lv);
    if(idx>maxIdx)maxIdx=idx;
    items.push({id:ok,name:obj.en,level:lv,evidence:obj.evidence?obj.evidence[framework]||[]:[]});
  }
  items.sort((a,b)=>levels.indexOf(b.level)-levels.indexOf(a.level));
  return{level:maxIdx>=0?levels[maxIdx]:unit.level,derived:maxIdx>=0,objectives:items};
};

